title: 2M Micro USB Cable, Micro USB to USB-A 2.0 Charging Cable, 480Mbps Hight-Speed Transfer, 5A Fast Charging, Pilot Lamp, Android Charger Cable for Samsung, LG, Nokia, Xbox,HTC,Sony, Kindle Fire
features: Rapid Charging and Data Syncing: With 5A fast charging capabilities, this cable ensures quick and efficient charging while meeting USB 2.0 standards. Enjoy data transfer speeds of up to 480 Mbps, making file sharing faster and more efficient.

Robust and Tangle-Free Design: Crafted with double-layer braided nylon fiber, the cable offers outstanding durability, strength, and flexibility. It’s designed to endure 10,000 bends at a 90-degree angle, preventing tangling and prolonging its lifespan. Your workspace stays neat and organized.

Premium Connectors: The connectors are made of high-quality aluminum alloy, providing resistance to corrosion and maintaining strong signal integrity. This results in more stable and reliable data transfers.

Convenient Green Indicator Light: A steady green indicator light helps you quickly locate your device, even in the dark. It’s especially useful when the lights are off, adding convenience to your charging experience.
Broad Compatibility: This Micro USB to USB-A charging cable is compatible with a wide range of devices, including Android smartphones, tablets, Kindle Fire, power banks, and headphones.
